# Teahouse consumer state (ADR-0014). The engine writes observability under
# .teahouse/ (logs + captured session Transcripts + Manifest), regenerated every
# Run; .env holds operator secrets sourced before a Run. The @ai-hero/sandcastle
# library creates sandbox checkouts under .sandcastle/worktrees/ at dispatch time.
.teahouse/logs/
.teahouse/sessions/
.teahouse/.env
.sandcastle/worktrees/
